{"name":"The Disciple","permission":{"default":0,"6CCGnEQyToQj7t5R":3},"type":"species","data":{"description":"<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Starting Experience</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>: </strong>100</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Starting Skills</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>:</strong> 1 rank in either </span><em>Discipline </em><span class=\"fontstyle2\">or <em>Coercion</em>.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Fervent Belief:</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"> Once per session, your character may spend <em>a Story Point</em> to decrease the difficulty of <em>a fear check</em> once, to a minimum of </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Simple (&ndash;)</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">. If the fear relates to his chosen cause, he may ignore it entirely.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Inspired Cohort:</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"> Once per session, your character may spend <strong>any number</strong> of<em> Story Points</em> as an incidental. If she does, that many chosen allies may use her ranks in <em>Discipline </em>instead of their own ranks in a chosen social skill for the remainder of the encounter, or until your character is incapacitated. Each character aided by this ability chooses a social skill separately.</span></p>","attributes":{"Brawn":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Brawn"},"Agility":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Agility"},"Intellect":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Intellect"},"Cunning":{"value":1,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Cunning"},"Willpower":{"value":3,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Willpower"},"Presence":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Presence"},"Wounds":{"value":10,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Wounds"},"Strain":{"value":10,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Strain"}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"HlZtMY0CvBu4jnZ0"}
{"name":"The Gymnast","permission":{"default":0,"6CCGnEQyToQj7t5R":3},"type":"species","data":{"description":"<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Starting Experience</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>:</strong> 100</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Adrenaline Rush:</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"> Once per session, your character may spend<em> a Story Point</em> to reduce all incoming strain by 2 for the duration of the current encounter. Afterthe encounter, he increases all incoming strain by 1 until completing a natural rest.</span></span></p>\n<p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Conditioned Reflexes:</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"> Once per session, your character may spend<em> a Story Point </em>during combat or another structured encounter to take an out-of-turn action (including an attack). She may not do so on her own turn and this extra action does not replace the action on her own turn.</span> <br style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: -webkit-auto; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\" /></span></p>","attributes":{"Brawn":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Brawn"},"Agility":{"value":3,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Agility"},"Intellect":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Intellect"},"Cunning":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Cunning"},"Willpower":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Willpower"},"Presence":{"value":1,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Presence"},"Wounds":{"value":11,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Wounds"},"Strain":{"value":9,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Strain"},"attr1626607313660":{"modtype":"Skill Rank","value":1,"mod":"Coordination"}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"bwh7pHIFDOCxKrQ6"}
{"name":"The Rascal","permission":{"default":0,"6CCGnEQyToQj7t5R":3},"type":"species","data":{"description":"<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Starting Experience</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>: </strong>100</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Starting Skills</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>:</strong> 1 rank in either <em>Deception </em>or <em>Charm</em>.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Lucky Break:</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"> Once per session, your character may spend <em>a Story Point</em> after failing any check to re-roll that check once, adding</span>&nbsp;[BO]<span class=\"fontstyle3\">&nbsp;</span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">to the re-roll.</span></p>\n<p><strong><span class=\"fontstyle0\">Work the Crowd:</span></strong><span class=\"fontstyle2\"> Once per session, your character may spend any number of Story Points to make a social check targeting a crowd as if the check were made against a single person. The crowd&rsquo;s size may not exceed 10 &times; Story Points spent.</span></p>","attributes":{"Brawn":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Brawn"},"Agility":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Agility"},"Intellect":{"value":1,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Intellect"},"Cunning":{"value":3,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Cunning"},"Willpower":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Willpower"},"Presence":{"value":2,"modtype":"Characteristic","mod":"Presence"},"Wounds":{"value":9,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Wounds"},"Strain":{"value":11,"modtype":"Stat","mod":"Strain"}}},"flags":{},"img":"icons/svg/mystery-man.svg","effects":[],"_id":"CTDIW2sqQ8Pki7gZ"}
